  <body>
    <segment id="1" parent="7" relname="span">Darwin as a Geologist</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="1" relname="concession">He tends to be viewed now as a biologist,</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="9" relname="span">but in his five years on the Beagle his main work was geology,</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="8" relname="span">and he saw himself as a geologist.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="4" relname="evidence">His work contributed significantly to the field.</segment>
